How to reference the images in flask?
It has to be inside the static/ folder, and you can use /static/SCREENSHOTS/img_01.png to reference it, for example.
Make sure your path is valid. You can either copy SCREENSHOTS to static/ folder, or make a soft link to it inside static/.



=======================
I am using mod_wsgi now

1 /etc/http/conf.d/miniblog.conf
2 /var/www/miniblog/miniblog.wsgi
3 /var/www/miniblog/app.py, I let it run on port 33333, which is important 
